title: Live updates: Rhett Lashlee reviews Auburn's win over Kentucky
text:
Auburn offensive coordinator Rhett Lashlee will meet with the media following Sunday's practice.
Lashlee went over Auburn's 30-27 over Kentucky and assess where the Tigers (4-2, 1-2 SEC) are offensively after halfway through the season.
Refresh this page for live updates.
RHETT LASHLEE
